prompts.frontCover:
Front cover of a greeting card, flat 2D illustration. The style is dreamy fantasy with a humorous, lighthearted tone.

The scene is a magical, whimsical beach at twilight. The sand is a soft, glowing gold, and the ocean has gentle, luminous turquoise waves that sparkle with bioluminescence. The sky is a gradient of deep indigo and soft lavender, dotted with constellations shaped like Chinese food items—a Great Dipper made of dumplings, a constellation of a spring roll, and another of a noodle bowl.

In the center of the scene, characters of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are having a surreal picnic on a large, floating lotus leaf instead of a blanket. They are illustrated in a cute cartoon style, wearing the same outfits from the photo (Lao Lao in her black puffer jacket, Jordan in his dark grey crewneck and black jacket, logos omitted). Both have joyful, laughing expressions.

Instead of a picnic basket, there's a giant, steaming Chinese takeout box between them, from which noodles and glowing stars comically spill out onto the lotus leaf. Jordan is playfully trying to catch a floating, giggling shrimp dumpling with his chopsticks. Lao Lao is laughing, holding a pair of chopsticks with a piece of glowing broccoli on the end. Little, friendly crabs with tiny lanterns on their backs scuttle around the edge of the lotus leaf.

Centered in the sky above them, written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script, is the text:
"Happy Anniversary, My Everything Dumpling"
